name: Pac-Man
description:
Pac-Man (パックマン Pakkuman, formerly known as Puck Man in Japan) is the titular main protagonist of the Pac-Man series, and is the mascot of Namco and its successor company, Bandai Namco Entertainment.

The three Pac-Man at the top depict the flag of Malaysia, while the one at the bottom depicts the flag of Ireland.
